humanMachineDialogue.text: According to the pathology report, 'Lymph nodes: 0/10 positive for metastasis (Axillary 0/10)'. This indicates that no lymph nodes have metastatic carcinoma. Therefore, based on New Rule 11, the N stage is N0.

humanMachineDialogue.text: The report indicates that 10 dissected lymph nodes were examined and all of them were negative for metastasis (Axillary 0/10). This corresponds to an N0 stage, which means no regional lymph node metastasis.
